<pb ed="T" id="T19.0964.0338b" n="0338b"/>
<lb n="0338b01"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0338b02"/><head type="no">No. 964</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0338b03"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0338001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本，【甲】黃檗版淨嚴等加筆本，此經宋元二本欠</note>佛說大威德金輪佛頂熾盛光如
<lb n="0338b04"/>來消除一切災難陀羅尼<note n="0338002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＋（九曜真言附）細註【明】【甲】</note><app n="0338002"><lem>經</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">經<note place="inline">九曜真言附</note></rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0338b05"/>
<lb n="0338b06"/><byline type="Translator">唐代失<note n="0338003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">譯＋（人名）【明】【甲】</note><app n="0338003"><lem>譯</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">譯人名</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0338b07"/><p>爾時釋迦牟尼佛。住淨居天宮。告文殊師利
<lb n="0338b08"/>菩薩摩訶薩。及諸四眾八部遊空大天九執
<lb n="0338b09"/>七曜十二宮神二十八星日月諸宿。我昔於
<lb n="0338b10"/>過去娑羅樹王佛所。受此大威德金輪佛頂
<lb n="0338b11"/>熾盛光如來消除一切災難陀羅尼法。於未
<lb n="0338b12"/>來世中若有國界。日月五星羅&CB00264;計都彗孛
<lb n="0338b13"/>妖怪惡星。照臨所屬本命宮宿及諸星位。或
<lb n="0338b14"/>臨帝座於國於家并分野處。陵逼之時或進
<lb n="0338b15"/>或入作諸災難者。應於清淨處置立道場。志
<lb n="0338b16"/>心持是陀羅尼<note n="0338004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔經〕－【明】【甲】</note><app n="0338004"><lem>經</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>一百八遍或一千八十遍。
<lb n="0338b17"/>若一日二日乃至七日。依法修<note n="0338005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">治＝持【明】【甲】</note><app n="0338005"><lem>治</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">持</rdg></app>壇場受持
<lb n="0338b18"/>讀誦。一切災難自然消<note n="0338006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">滅＝散【明】【甲】</note><app n="0338006"><lem>滅</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">散</rdg></app>不能為害。若<note n="0338007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＝太【明】【甲】</note><app n="0338007"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">太</rdg></app>
<lb n="0338b19"/>白火星入於南斗。於國於家及分野處作災
<lb n="0338b20"/>難者。應於一忿怒尊像前。畫彼設<note n="0338008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00418;＝都【明】【甲】</note><app n="0338008"><lem>&CB00418;</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">都</rdg></app>嚕形。
<lb n="0338b21"/>念此真言加持。其災即散移於不順王命悖
<lb n="0338b22"/>逆人身上。即說陀羅尼真言曰</p>
<lb n="0338b23"/><p type="dharani">喃<note n="0338009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無去＝謨去聲【明】【甲】</note><app n="0338009"><lem>無<note place="inline">去</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">謨去聲</rdg></app>三滿哆沒馱喃阿&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底<note place="inline">丁以<note n="0338010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">反＝切【明】【甲】</note><app n="0338010"><lem>反</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">切</rdg></app></note>賀
<lb n="0338b24"/>哆舍薩曩喃<note place="inline">引</note>唵<note place="inline">引</note>佉佉佉呬佉呬吽<note n="0338011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔半音〕－【明】【甲】</note><app n="0338011"><lem><note place="inline">半音</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>吽
<lb n="0338b25"/>入&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>囉入&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>囉&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>入&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>囉&CB00425;
<lb n="0338b26"/>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>入&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>囉底瑟吒<note place="inline">二合</note>底瑟吒<note place="inline">二合</note>瑟緻
<lb n="0338b27"/><note place="inline">二合</note>哩瑟緻<note place="inline">二合</note>哩薩<note n="0338012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">發＝癹【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0338012"><lem>發</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">癹</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>吒薩<anchor id="fxT19p0338b01"/>發<note place="inline">二合</note>吒扇
<lb n="0338b28"/>底迦室哩<note place="inline">二合</note>曳娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0338b29"/><p>佛言若國界分野及男子女人。被諸天星辰
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0964.0338c" n="0338c"/>
<lb n="0338c01"/>所臨身形。但書寫此經志心受持讀誦。常須
<lb n="0338c02"/>護淨。此陀羅尼一切如來同共宣說。能成就
<lb n="0338c03"/>八萬種大吉祥事。復能<note n="0338013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">滅除＝除滅【明】【甲】</note><app n="0338013"><lem>滅除</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">除滅</rdg></app>八萬種大不吉
<lb n="0338c04"/>祥事。若有國王大臣及諸眷屬一切庶民。或
<lb n="0338c05"/>被五星羅&CB00264;計都彗孛怪惡諸宿。陵逼帝座
<lb n="0338c06"/>於國於家并分野處所屬宮宿。災難競起。或
<lb n="0338c07"/>土星侵陵或進或退。及宿世<note n="0338014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">怨＝冤【甲】</note><app n="0338014"><lem>怨</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">冤</rdg></app>家欲相謀害。
<lb n="0338c08"/>諸惡橫事口舌厭禱&CB00057;詛符書以為災難。令
<lb n="0338c09"/>諸眾生依法受持。一切災禍不能為害。變災
<lb n="0338c10"/>為福皆得吉祥。我說此真言不可思議功德
<lb n="0338c11"/>無比。祕密受持勿妄宣傳。佛告大眾若有國
<lb n="0338c12"/>界不安災難起時。及男子女人災<note n="0338015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">詳＝祥【明】【甲】</note><app n="0338015"><lem>詳</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">祥</rdg></app>變禍。但
<lb n="0338c13"/>請僧眾如法建立道場安置佛像<note n="0338016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">潔戒＝結果【明】【甲】</note><app n="0338016"><lem>潔戒</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">結果</rdg></app>護持。
<lb n="0338c14"/>香花燈燭隨分供養。令諸眾生獲福無量其
<lb n="0338c15"/>災即除</p>
<lb n="0338c16"/><p>爾時如來復告大眾。若人行年被金木水火
<lb n="0338c17"/>土五星。及羅&CB00264;計都日月諸宿臨身。災難競
<lb n="0338c18"/>起。我有大吉祥真言名破宿曜。若能受持志
<lb n="0338c19"/>心憶念。其災自滅變禍為福。即說真言曰</p>
<lb n="0338c20"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引</note>薩&CB00085;諾剎<note n="0338017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">咀＝呾【明】【甲】</note><app n="0338017"><lem>咀</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">呾</rdg></app>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>糝摩曳室哩曳扇底
<lb n="0338c21"/><note n="0338018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">迦＋（囉）【甲】</note><app n="0338018"><lem>迦</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">迦囉</rdg></app><note n="0338019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">呴嚧＝句嚕【明】【甲】</note><app n="0338019"><lem>呴嚧</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">句嚕</rdg></app>薩婆訶</p>
<lb n="0338c22"/><p>爾時如來說是經<note n="0338020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">時＝已【明】【甲】</note><app n="0338020"><lem>時</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">已</rdg></app>。文殊師利菩薩摩訶薩。
<lb n="0338c23"/>及諸四眾遊空大天諸星辰等一切聖眾。咸
<lb n="0338c24"/>依佛&CB00330;頂禮奉<note n="0338021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">持＝行【明】【甲】</note><app n="0338021"><lem>持</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">行</rdg></app>各還本宮。天龍八部等聞
<lb n="0338c25"/>佛所說。皆大歡喜信受奉行</p>
<lb n="0338c26"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>佛說<note n="0338022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（大威德金輪佛頂）＋熾【明】【甲】</note><app n="0338022"><lem>熾</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">大威德金輪佛頂熾</rdg></app>盛光<note n="0338023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">消災＝如來消除一切難陀羅尼【明】【甲】</note><app n="0338023"><lem>消災</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">如來消除一切難陀羅尼</rdg></app>經</jhead></juan></div1><div1 type="W">
<lb n="0338c27"/><p>九曜真言曰</p>
<lb n="0338c28"/><p>金</p><p type="dharani">曩謨三滿<note n="0338024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">跢＝多【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0338024"><lem>跢</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">多</rdg></app>沒馱喃唵<note place="inline">引</note>摩<note n="0338025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賀咸＝訶戍【明】【甲】</note><app n="0338025"><lem>賀咸</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">訶戍</rdg></app>尾<note n="0338026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔微一反〕－【明】【甲】</note><app n="0338026"><lem><note place="inline">微一
<lb n="0338c29"/>反</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>野<note n="0338027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">娑&CB00085;二合賀引＝莎訶【明】【甲】</note><app n="0338027"><lem>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">莎訶</rdg></app></p>
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0964.0339a" n="0339a"/>
<lb n="0339a01"/><p>木</p><p type="dharani">曩謨三滿<anchor id="fxT19p0339a01"/>跢沒馱喃唵<note place="inline">引</note>印<note n="0339001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔上〕－【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0339001"><lem><note place="inline">上</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0339002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00178;＝捺【明】【甲】</note><app n="0339002"><lem>&CB00178;</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">捺</rdg></app>囉
<lb n="0339a02"/><note n="0339003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合〕－【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0339003"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>野娑<note n="0339004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00085;二合賀引＝訶【明】【甲】</note><app n="0339004"><lem>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">訶</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0339a03"/><p>水</p><p type="dharani">曩謨三滿<anchor id="fxT19p0339a02"/>跢沒馱喃唵<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00085;<note n="0339005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔無可反〕－【明】【甲】</note><app n="0339005"><lem><note place="inline">無可反</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>嚕拏
<lb n="0339a04"/><anchor id="fxT19p0339a03"/><note place="inline">上</note>野娑&CB00085;<anchor id="fxT19p0339a04"/><note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0339006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賀引＝訶【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0339006"><lem>賀<note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">訶</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0339a05"/><p>火</p><p type="dharani">曩謨三滿<anchor id="fxT19p0339a05"/>跢沒馱喃唵<note place="inline">引</note>阿<anchor id="fxT19p0339a06"/><note place="inline">上</note><note n="0339007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">仡＝乞【明】【甲】</note><app n="0339007"><lem>仡</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">乞</rdg></app>曩
<lb n="0339a06"/><anchor id="fxT19p0339a07"/><note place="inline">上</note>曳娑&CB00085;<anchor id="fxT19p0339a08"/><note place="inline">二合</note><anchor id="fxT19p0339a09"/>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0339a07"/><p>土</p><p type="dharani">曩謨三滿<anchor id="fxT19p0339a10"/>跢沒馱喃唵<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00425;囉<anchor id="fxT19p0339a11"/><note place="inline">二合</note>替
<lb n="0339a08"/><anchor id="fxT19p0339a12"/><note place="inline">上</note>曳娑&CB00085;<anchor id="fxT19p0339a13"/><note place="inline">二合</note><anchor id="fxT19p0339a14"/>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
